      "content": "i know i should reach out but what's the point? everyone just says the same thing and it doesn't change the fact that my entire life was built around someone who isn't even here anymore. it's like the air is gone. i look at my bedroom and i just see a graveyard of everything we had. it feels more real than anything else. i just want the noise to stop.",
